lyTime":"2021-03-26T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"搵到啲野一年以上無用過已經想dump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍唔到手唔dump佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:21:27.000Z","msg":"扔哂佢<br />\n垃圾係應該去垃圾桶<br />\n舊記憶應該刪走再沒留憑證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:34:46.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得冇勇氣面對過去既回憶既人<br />\n或者個人本身好沉溺過去，先要靠掉走以前既物品去迫自己放低過去<br />\n我覺得斷捨離本身唔應該被視為逃避過去既手段。當下既自己係由過去既回憶組成。<br />\n<br />\n當然若果個case係乜野狗屎垃圾都留，留到冇位擺野，影響生活就另計。"},{"pid":"5f5d24816a28a5e684af2281a1cf8570e96b733a","tid":2462173,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />剪撚晒同ex 所有野好撚爽"},{"pid":"d6450dd959a92919ea35f5b7ad9d7685dc368928","tid":2462173,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:36:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"989ce895b6473ba3261d3a8ae43de59ea95c8730","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a6604a002b29b50b91d7214f44ac05a00d315e7","tid":2462173,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:29:06.000Z","msg":"清極都好似仲有<br />\n特別係衫褲袋<br />\n清哂唔用既化妝品 化妝掃<br />\n文具反而冇乜<br />\n<br />\n黎緊搬屋再清多獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想新屋係極簡主義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"化妝品我都扔埋 ，留一盒最貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能因為陪條賤人去買<br />\n我扔得好灑脫。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一招如果係大地色可以做埋眉粉清得快d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔得就加水畫下畫咁<br />\n想清屋既話都要直接扔。"},{"pid":"c4f6d3dc9ef88b4a37f2decad4d6bc6963fbdad9","tid":2462173,"uid":233071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"抄字典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no